Head of Compliance, Abu Dhabi, 10+ Years PQE
Head of Compliance, Abu Dhabi, 10+ Years PQE
Location:  --Abu Dhabi
Our client is a leading defence manufacturer with close links to the UAE government and global contracts and clients.
They are looking to employ their first Head of Compliance.  The role will entail building and managing the entire compliance offering for the company, which includes health and safety; export control and compliance on the broadest scale.  Answering only to the General Counsel this is an extremely senior and important role and one of the most attractive compliance roles available in the Middle East at present.
Applicants must have at least 10 years of broad, compliance experience.  Experience of working in the Middle East would be an advantage.
For further details, please contact Iain Rainey; send your CV and covering email to
